check.critical:
Required story JSON fields before status change to done:
        - content.fileList: { created: string[], modified: string[], deleted: string[] }
        - content.changeLog: Array<{ date: string, summary: string }>
        - content.devAgentRecord: { implementationNotes: string[], completionNotes: string[], debugLog: string[] }
        If any are missing, add them now before proceeding.

step.output:
**✅ Review Complete!**

      **Story Status:** {{new_status}}
      **Issues Fixed:** {{fixed_count}}
      **Action Items Created:** {{action_count}}

      {{#if new_status == "done"}}Code review complete!{{else}}Address the action items and continue development.{{/if}}
